Description:
    Generates a new Me Salva! customized model spec at spec/models.
    Pass the model name as an argument, either CamelCased or snake_cased.
    It is possible to pass the attributes arguments as well.

Examples:
    `bin/rails generate ms_model_spec Awesome`
    `bin/rails generate ms_model_spec Awesome attribute1:string attribute2:integer attribute3:references`

    creates a Me Salva! customized awesome model spec:
        spec/models/awesome_spec.rb
